<LanguageData>
  
  <!-- EN: phased-array radar -->
  <DMSE_PhaseArrayRadar.label>相控陣雷達</DMSE_PhaseArrayRadar.label>
  <!-- EN: A multi-purpose radar used for early warning and fire control targeting, typically installed on ships or military bases to track moving objects in the surrounding space. It can effectively identify the trajectories of suborbital objects such as droppods and predict their descent locations in advance; however, it is extremely power-intensive. -->
  <DMSE_PhaseArrayRadar.description>一種用於預警與火控瞄準的多用途雷達，通常被安裝於艦船或軍事基地追蹤周圍空間內的活動物體。能夠有效識別空降艙等亞軌道飛行物體的軌跡並提前預測其下落位置，能夠為基地的預警及提前部署提供寶貴的反應時間，然而十分消耗電力。</DMSE_PhaseArrayRadar.description>
  
  <!-- EN: signal stealth device -->
  <DMSE_StealthDevice.label>訊號匿蹤裝置</DMSE_StealthDevice.label>
  <!-- EN: A massive plasma field generator, widely used by the colonial fleet in automated orbital facilities, effectively shielding against internal life signals, effectively cloaking the device in space and rendering it invisible to active radar.\n\nInternal life signals increase the device's power consumption, requiring a day to cool and recharge after successful shielding. -->
  <DMSE_StealthDevice.description>一種巨大的等離子場護盾發生器，能夠有效屏蔽訊號產生，並透過定向抵銷雷達波，使外部無法搜尋到發生器所在的小行星基地。\n\n但要注意，內部活體訊號越多，設備耗電越高；且每次成功阻止一次雷達搜尋後，都需要一天時間冷卻並重新充能。</DMSE_StealthDevice.description>
  
</LanguageData>